com.threerings.nexus.server
Class ObjectManager

java.lang.Object
  com.threerings.nexus.server.ObjectManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventSink
public class ObjectManager
extends Object
implements EventSink

Maintains metadata for all registered entities including their contexts. Contexts are action queues that are guaranteed to be processed in a single-threaded manner.

Nested Class Summary
static interface ObjectManager.Subscriber
          An interface implemented by sessions, which must forward object events to clients.
